      <p class="text-stone-600 mb-8">Last Updated: 23 September 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">
        <p class="mb-6">
          This Privacy Policy explains how Petal Culture (ABN 70 508 300 665) ("we", "our", "us")
          handles your personal information when you interact with us online, in-office, or via other
          channels. We are committed to protecting your privacy in accordance with the Privacy Act
