          <li><strong>Demographic information:</strong> gender, date of birth, interests.</li>
          <li><strong>Purchase and transaction details:</strong> products ordered, payment and billing information.</li>
          <li><strong>Device and usage data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, cookies, and location data.</li>
          <li><strong>Other information:</strong> preferences, feedback, allergy details (if you provide them), or any information you voluntarily share with us.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Collect Your Personal Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We collect personal information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
