              <li>Place an order online or via telephone.</li>
              <li>Contact us via phone, email, chat, social media, or online forms.</li>
              <li>Subscribe to our mailing list.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Automatically,</strong> via cookies and website tracking tools.</li>
          <li><strong>From third parties,</strong> such as service providers, advertising partners, or publicly available sources.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8 mb-4">3. Why We Collect, Use and Disclose Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use your personal information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
