          <li>Respond to your enquiries, feedback, or complaints.</li>
          <li>Send order confirmations, receipts, and account communications.</li>
          <li>Improve our websites, services, and customer experience.</li>
          <li>Carry out business operations, analysis, and reporting.</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations or resolve disputes.</li>
