        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We may also use third-party tools (e.g. Google Analytics) for performance and marketing
          tracking. These tools may collect information via their own cookies. We do not control how
          these third parties handle your information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8 mb-4">5. Sharing Your Personal Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We may share your personal information with:</p>
