          <li>Advisors such as accountants, lawyers, and auditors.</li>
          <li>Third parties when required by law or authorised by you.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We require all third parties to handle your personal information in accordance with Australian
          privacy law.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8 mb-4">6. Sensitive Information</h2>
